specified in the Ada 95 Reference Manual.  In addition, GNAT implements
the implementation-defined pragmas from DEC Ada 83.

   * AST_ENTRY

   * COMMON_OBJECT

   * COMPONENT_ALIGNMENT

   * EXPORT_EXCEPTION

   * EXPORT_FUNCTION

   * EXPORT_OBJECT

