Restrictions on the Pragma SYSTEM_NAME
--------------------------------------

For DEC Ada for OpenVMS Alpha, the enumeration literal for the type
NAME is OPENVMS_AXP. In GNAT, the enumeration literal for the type NAME
is SYSTEM_NAME_GNAT.


